---
title: "Taxi Agency Website"
---

Taxi Agency Management System was developed using

ASP.NET Web Forms • C# • MySQL • phpMyAdmin

It simulates the workflow of a real taxi agency, including users, drivers, employees, managers, and administrators. The system covers all operations required to run a taxi service from customer trip requests to driver acceptance, billing, HR, maintenance, and travel management.

The project includes multiple user roles, each with dedicated functionality and custom dashboards.
<br>
Key Features:
<br>
1. Unified Login System<br>
2. User (Customer) Features<br>
3. Driver Features<br>
4. HR Department<br>
5. Travel Department<br>
6. Finance Department<br>
7. Maintenance Department<br>
8. Administrator Features<br>
9. Database<br>




